This is Perl module Github::IRCBot.

INSTALLATION

Github::IRCBot installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan Github::IRCBot

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Github::IRCBot documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Github::IRCBot

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

